data.description: Welcome to this stunning home located in the desirable Covington Chase neighborhood of Milton, DE. Situated on a spacious .78 acre lot, this property offers both privacy and tranquility. Step inside and be greeted by an inviting interior that boasts an array of impressive features. The first floor showcases a luxurious primary bedroom complete with a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom, providing a peaceful sanctuary to unwind after a long day. The main level also includes a formal dining room, a great room perfect for entertaining guests, a powder room, a laundry room, and an eat-in kitchen making this home perfect for entertaining.  Venture upstairs to discover two guest bedrooms and a second-floor bathroom, offering ample space for family and friends. Additionally, there is a generously sized bonus bedroom that can serve as another bedroom or be transformed into an incredible bonus room to suit your needs. As an added bonus, this home features a full basement, ideal for additional living space and storage. The basement includes another full bathroom, a large recreation room for endless entertainment possibilities, and an unfinished storage area for all your belongings.  The exterior of the property is equally impressive, with the home sitting on a .78-acre lot. The expansive backyard provides plenty of room for outdoor activities and offers endless possibilities for creating your own personal oasis. Sit back and relax on the paver patio after a long day at the beach! Conveniently located just 7 miles from Lewes Beach, this home allows you to enjoy the coastal lifestyle with ease. Spend your days lounging on the sandy shores or exploring the charming shops and restaurants nearby. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the best of Milton living in Covington Chase.
